logical-feed-as-twitter-burns-to-the-ground-152817251.html">Threads</a> （已在印度尼西亚推出）。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/indonesia-is-blocking-elon-musks-x-domain-for-its-gambling-and-porn-history-195551771.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/indonesia-is-blocking-elon-musks-x-domain-for-its-gambling-and-porn-history-195551771.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 98607b97-db24-4193-a4df-305357c64be7</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jul 2023 19:55:51 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690401469</ingested><modified> 2023-07-26T19:57:52+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3307" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3f4c0460-2b18-11ee-9dff-f4b79eb1981e" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3307" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3f4c0460-2b18-11ee-9dff-f4b79eb1981e" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[SOPA Images via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[UKRAINE - 2023/07/25: In this photo illustration, the new Twitter logo rebranded as X (X Corp.) is seen on a smartphone and Elon Musk Twitter account with the new X logo on a pc screen. (Photo Illustration by Pavlo Gonchar/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[In this photo illustration, the new Twitter logo rebranded...]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[SEC: Public companies must report cyberattacks within four days]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>为了防止上市公司推迟有关网络攻击的消息，<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.sec.gov/news/press-release/2023-139">美国安全交易委员会</a>设定了四天的最后期限来披露“重大网络安全事件”。如果美国司法部长可能会推迟披露，如果这样做会导致“国家安全或公共安全面临重大风险”。否则，这些规则将成为一个严格的新路标——尽管其限制性略低于欧盟 GDPR 网络攻击<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://gdpr-info.eu/art-34-gdpr/">期限（三天）</a> 。</p><p>此前，微软因<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-confirms-june-outlook-and-onedrive-outages-were-caused-by-ddos-attacks-173431319.html">花费数周时间才确认 Outlook 和其他在线服务遭受攻击而</a>受到安全专家的批评。 “如果微软不提供这些信息，我们真的无法衡量[攻击]的影响，”网络安全研究员、前美国国家安全局黑客杰克·威廉姆斯 (Jake Williams) 6 月份<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:CNBC;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=34e37b9c-8975-48da-aa39-df8bcd5badc3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=CNBC&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXHyS1BHXX8_Whc_yww-taFJbW_PMys1lpjwBf4hbiKW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F06%2F17%2Fmicrosoft-says-early-june-disruptions-to-outlook-cloud-platform-were-cyberattacks.html" class="rapid-with-clickid">告诉<em>美联社</em></a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>虽然 GDPR 规则更多的是为了保护公众，但 SEC 似乎更关注投资者：“目前，许多上市公司向投资者提供网络安全披露，”SEC 主席加里·根斯勒 (Gary Gensler) 在一份声明中表示。“我认为公司和投资者都一样，然而，如果这种披露以更加一致、可比和对决策有用的方式进行，将会受益。”</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-07-26/companies-have-4-day-deadline-to-report-hacks-in-final-sec-rule?sref=10lNAhZ9"><em>据彭博社</em>报道</a>，自去年首次宣布美国证券交易委员会的规则以来，科技公司一直在反对这些规则，最终导致其中包含了延迟条款。此外，信息技术产业委员会认为，四天的期限太短，因为届时公司可能对网络攻击还不够了解。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sec-public-companies-must-report-cyberattacks-within-four-days-193713534.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sec-public-companies-must-report-cyberattacks-within-four-days-193713534.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f0ac808a-c627-4cc9-8a80-9c41745219c3</guid><dc:creator>德文德拉·哈达瓦尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jul 2023 19:37:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690400234</ingested><modified> 2023-07-26T19:37:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Devindra Hardawar]]></category><media:content height="4320" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/aaac3c20-2bea-11ee-9bef-1343efd86759" width="7680"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4320" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/aaac3c20-2bea-11ee-9bef-1343efd86759" width="7680"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Sean Anthony Eddy via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Hacker, IT and person with code on computer, programming and phishing scam with malware or virus. Hacking, system glitch and cloud computing error in dark room, cyber crime and cybersecurity fail]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Hacker, IT and person with code on computer, programming and phishing scam with malware or virus. Hacking, system glitch and cloud com